{"tid":1853932,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中共不滿五星病毒旗 丹麥總理：我們有言論自由","createTime":"2020-01-31T08:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T09:16:17.000Z","uid":242537,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"28d4b5c6838f4dfb4cd93f55bf143a91e64497d3","tid":1853932,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T08:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqnDDzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqnDDzz.jpg&h=623aceb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqnDDzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqnDDzz.jpg&h=623aceb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqnDDzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqnDDzz.jpg&h=623aceb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqnDDzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqnDDzz.jpg&h=623aceb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqnDDzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqnDDzz.jpg&h=623aceb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqnDDzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqnDDzz.jpg&h=623aceb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqnDDzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqnDDzz.jpg&h=623aceb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqnDDzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqnDDzz.jpg&h=623aceb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqnDDzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqnDDzz.jpg&h=623aceb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqnDDzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqnDDzz.jpg&h=623aceb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqnDDzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqnDDzz.jpg&h=623aceb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqnDDzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqnDDzz.jpg&h=623aceb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【大紀元2020年01月29日訊】丹麥「日德蘭郵報」於當地時間27日出刊的諷刺漫畫，將中國國旗上的5星換成5枚新型冠狀病毒，引發中共要求丹麥道歉。丹麥總理佛瑞德里克森今天（當地時間28日）首度回應此事，表示：「我們有言論自由」。<br />\n<br />\n中央社引丹麥「地方報」（The Local）報導，中共駐丹麥大使館昨天（當地時間27日）要求「日德蘭郵報」（Jyllands-Posten）道歉。<br />\n<br />\n「日德蘭郵報」報導，佛瑞德里克森（Mette Frederiksen）今天（當地時間28日）在出席社會民主黨（Social Democratic Party）會議前，簡短對此事置評。<br />\n<br />\n佛瑞德里克森說：「丹麥在言論自由和諷刺畫作上，都有根深柢固的傳統，而這項傳統未來也會持續下去。這是丹麥的立場，眾所皆知，我們不會改變它。對於這件事，我除了以上沒有其它想說的。」<br />\n<br />\n中共要求丹麥道歉，但佛瑞德里克森並未直接回應這項要求。她說：「我們想說的是，丹麥擁有言論自由，也可以自由繪畫。」<br />\n<br />\n佛瑞德里克森表示，她所發表的言論，可被視為她對於丹麥在言論自由立場一事上的「官方聲明」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/534a33/f/800x0/https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Untitled-1-01_28Igl_1200x630cropcenter.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F534a33%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FUntitled-1-01_28Igl_1200x630cropcenter.png&h=a2bb4fb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddd4e9dc12c01b123af285b3e4b604afdef81ca2","tid":1853932,"uid":240606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:02:48.000Z","msg":"回"},{"pid":"b70e08e4adc0ae9bc268e8e3e23233b719f2b051","tid":1853932,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205ec6bd5b78c084ec167c1b931618e8f1e13dcd","tid":1853932,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T09:06:22.000Z","msg":"出解放軍囉 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41dbd69d80f32c1b3d6712af7fec63ce35e28b6","tid":1853932,"uid":289978,"like":1,